      },
      "flashin": {
        "alpha": [
          1,
          0
        ],
        "black": false,
        "delay": 1,
        "dur": 1
      },
      "say": "摯愛的人啊，我究竟是何顏色？",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgmDelay": 2,
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 401460,
      "side": 2,
      "say": "請妳告訴我。究竟妳期望的“我”，是什麼樣的？",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 401460,
      "side": 2,
      "say": "我會試著成為，妳所希望的那個存在。",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "——“46只要，做46自己就好”",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "我得到了答案。",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 401460,
      "side": 2,
      "say": "我的顏色…應是白色（Weiß）。",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 401460,
      "side": 2,
      "say": "為染上妳的顏色，將原本透明的自身染為白色的愚昧之“物”——",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 401460,
      "side": 2,
      "say": "要成為縱使無數次滿身戰爭的硝煙，也將洗盡心中灰色的“人”。",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "向著這誓言，向著眼前的“指揮官”，獻上力所能及的所有。",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "話語、擁抱、親吻。一切一切的祝福。",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 401460,
      "side": 2,
